{"tid":586549,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"地球人都知道Sigma防震垃撚圾","createTime":"2018-03-09T15:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T03:54:05.000Z","uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa007d5639f231816bb012dbc833362649f7bf1b","tid":586549,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/198233/攝影師-steffen-jahn-表示：因-sigma-art-鏡頭穩定器的設計缺陷，破/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F198233%2F%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%B8%AB-steffen-jahn-%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%A0-sigma-art-%E9%8F%A1%E9%A0%AD%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7%EF%BC%8C%E7%A0%B4%2F&d=RCy%2F34UwP%2Bv8XPXFD%2BhNptWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=a733a8fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/198233/攝影師-steffen-jahn-表示：因-sigma-art-鏡頭穩定器的設計缺陷，破/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/231229_dc2074fc0cbf8a372074ce2c3fc6959e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F231229_dc2074fc0cbf8a372074ce2c3fc6959e.png&h=b2d6255c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攝影師 Steffen Jahn 擁有超過 20 年拍攝汽車的經驗，曾與保時捷、法拉利、林寶堅尼等品牌合作。最近，他在網上分享了一次為《Top Gear》雜誌拍攝「Ferrari 488 Pista」汽車時，因 Sigma 鏡頭穩定器的設計缺陷，而未能拍到滿意作品的經歷。<br />\n<br />\nSteffen 當天選用了 Nikon D850 相機及 Sigma Art 24-105mm f/4 Art 鏡頭來拍攝。他用了這支鏡頭兩個月，一直都很滿意其質素，事前認為是今次拍攝的「完美搭配」。<br />\n<br />\n雜誌編輯要求 Steffen 在 6 小時內拍到 12 張以上高質素的照片，他當天為了避開陳列室內的燈光反射，用了自己的 Elinchrom 400B 閃光燈，配合多重曝光來拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n拍完第一輪之後，他開始檢查照片，發現汽車在不同照片的畫面內「跳上跳下」，他起初以為這是因為木地板的搖晃，在第二輪拍攝時便特別小心腳步，沒有走得太近，但出來的照片仍然很不穩定。由於時間緊迫，他只好繼續拍攝，希望之後可以用 Photoshop 救回照片。<br />\n<br />\n拍攝完成後幾天，Steffen 聯絡 Sigma 客戶服務部問問到底發生了甚麼事，得到的回覆是：即使將鏡頭的影像穩定器（Optical Stabilizer）關掉，也不代表這真的關閉了，穩定元件會因為磁場而影響位置，當關閉相機時，穩定元件會向下移動，開啟相機後穩定元件就需要一些時間來回復位置，即使只在進行拍攝，這過程也不會停下來。<br />\n<br />\nSigma Germany 為 Steffen 的鏡頭進行檢查，並更新了影像穩定器的元件，但同樣問題仍舊出現，所以他就只好將鏡頭放到 eBay 出售了。是次分享引起了不少討論，大家使用 Sigma 鏡頭時也有遇過這種情況嗎？"},{"pid":"e55e96cc8d26c681fb7c7727e6a807633185ffb6","tid":586549,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"所以我幾時都話定無買Sigma<br />\n防震靠Tamron"},{"pid":"712c9ce923cb46324db47b097cf85cc61c87131f","tid":586549,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"所以我幾時都話定焦買Sigma<br />\n防震靠Tamron"},{"pid":"ce0feb094e2c50b3f34e90bd258749468fbabf22","tid":586549,"uid":28001,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"712c9ce923cb46324db47b097cf85cc61c87131f","tid":586549,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"所以我幾時都話定焦買Sigma<br />\n防震靠Tamron"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"幾時都話買鏡買原廠"},{"pid":"f0e1f10dde32ff10d57f61b47c3e0059475c5327","tid":586549,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ce0feb094e2c50b3f34e90bd258749468fbabf22","tid":586549,"uid":28001,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"712c9ce923cb46324db47b097cf85cc61c87131f","tid":586549,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"所以我幾時都話定焦買Sigma<br />\n防震靠Tamron"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"幾時都話買鏡買原廠"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T19:22:51.000Z","msg":"窮撚無錢，又想派頭勁<br />\nSigma其實都係原廠黎既"},{"pid":"0a7fe772e74e1531ba7b974667844b49bba5e832","tid":586549,"uid":40672,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ce0feb094e2c50b3f34e90bd258749468fbabf22","tid":586549,"uid":28001,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"712c9ce923cb46324db47b097cf85cc61c87131f","tid":586549,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:14:35.000Z","msg":"所以我幾時都話定焦買Sigma<br />\n防震靠Tamron"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"幾時都話買鏡買原廠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T19:24:18.000Z","msg":"龍仔VC世界第一"},{"pid":"cb00441244b5f13836d87e8a5a63b4dc7e780700","tid":58